                    perspiciatis totam et nisi qui repellendus eum laboriosam rem corrupti reiciendis officia 
                    quidem quibusdam quas quos temp.
                </p>                
                <div class="products-new">
                    <a href="/producto/editar/<%= newProducts.id %>">
                        <article>
                            <div class="img-description">
                                <img src="/images/products/<%- newProducts.images[0] ? newProducts.images[0].name : 'no-image-available.jpg' %>" alt="No Image"
                            class="product-image" class="product-image">
